✈️ British Airways Review Dashboard – Tableau

An interactive Tableau dashboard analyzing British Airways customer reviews and ratings to uncover insights on service quality, customer satisfaction, and regional trends.

🔑 Features

📊 Visualized customer ratings across different service categories (cabin crew, seating, food & beverages, etc.)

🌍 Regional and category-wise review distribution

⭐ Trend analysis of customer satisfaction levels

🔎 Identified key improvement areas through data storytelling

🛠️ Tech Stack

Tableau for data visualization

Excel/CSV as data source

📈 Learning Outcomes

Enhanced skills in data visualization, storytelling, and dashboard design

Applied analytics to real-world airline customer experience data
